{"tid":1391884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報 大力支持","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:15:56.000Z","uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df5f9aa81b56b7bcbfae3c69c6757c9a2a3d792c","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"標題黨麻煩睇吓先<br />\n<br />\n啱啱我大陸個表弟問我究竟發生乜嘢事<br />\n香港做咩會突然間咁亂 <br />\n用佢嘅（亂）表示<br />\n亂左咁耐而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我就同佢講左好多嘢<br />\n包括光復香港時代革命第一日到而家<br />\n跟住下面嗰條link佢就問我可以點樣解釋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/a0zwHEDeVSgfKts5y3YRjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fa0zwHEDeVSgfKts5y3YRjQ&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=6bab0b56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/a0zwHEDeVSgfKts5y3YRjQ</a><br />\n<br />\n下面一條片搞掂左上面呢條link <br />\n<br />\n當然我唔能夠話我表弟係冇腦 <br />\n只可以話人民日報實在太好<br />\n我都忍唔住入去cap左張圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cuspcusp/videos/434000713856128/?hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcuspcusp%2Fvideos%2F434000713856128%2F%3Fhc_location%3Dufi&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=77828a63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cuspcusp/videos/434000713856128/?hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n<br />\n你哋可以睇下佢哋有幾咁可悲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BoXQGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BoXQGG.png&h=75837e1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"131cd2e75df08265f53d5071a34f29021f741f6d","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察已經克制到無可忍耐的地步</span></span>"},{"pid":"922876ebf0b4d124975690c90ac530c86b92c56b","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"ea9553f6534d997e35a9315730bb6afff3a4320e","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"53f9542398780c2de3c4cba2e1a2ad1963f28cb9","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"我要睇人民日報"},{"pid":"aeaa6f66fc083d755bd0bc68fa4f3e676af04f5b","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"屌晒佢老母"},{"pid":"8d950ef62eca050e3e3929fba49e97fb8d2d751f","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"b9ad6781ef7cc3980d65898df4eef960aee211d5","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"推比人哋睇"},{"pid":"468fa415f26bf5f12d1b2994382e953e0aa39cfb","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"偉大嘅 人民日報"},{"pid":"94f81c139eb6c653e6e3e7f3bb94afbe8d2b2a05","tid":1391884,"uid":247930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"大陸新聞"},{"pid":"4b3731f9d78712dab407538cc79e7281cc20e811","tid":1391884,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"微信公眾號，個admin係逐個逐個回覆放出黎的，一般唔會放相反意見出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a9f5209fdb7a291f3d313070848b974364bfc5","tid":1391884,"uid":38482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2